name: Sterling Silver Leaf Silhouette Earrings
description:
These handmade sterling silver leaf shaped earrings have an organic, chic vibe. They hang from a simple sterling ear wire. These striking earrings measure just under 3" from top of ear wire to bottom of earring. You are sure to be noticed wearing these statement earrings.

The first pair of these earrings was purchased from my cousin as shown in last image. You will receive the pair of earrings shown in the other images.
